    <detaileddescription>
<para>Draw command can be attached to the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Renderer" kindref="compound">Dali::Renderer</ref> and override the default rendering functionality. <ref refid="classDali_1_1Renderer" kindref="compound">Renderer</ref> may have several DrawCommands attached to it and the will be executed sequentially in the order of the &apos;queue&apos; index. </para>
